Run the program with active_sports_stats.py. That should allow the user to make
an inquiry about a skier and/or enter a new skier. One element of Hard Mode
is included: Ability to update existing data. After looking up
a skier, the user is given the chance to update the team country name.

ski_stats is the original data file.

sports_stats_migration.py is the file used to read the original data into the
database.
